Package: MODIS
Type: Package
Title: MODIS Acquisition and Processing
Version: 0.10-28
Date: 2015-06-15
Depends: R (>= 2.10), utils, raster
Suggests: RCurl, rgeos, rgdal, bitops, mapdata, XML, parallel, ptw
